clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#寫得好好💛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你老公九成時間都好愛你<br />\n剩低一成時間就背叛你，晚晚都搵不同女人上床<br />\n咁你接唔接受到？<br />\n會唔會話佢戴套咪得囉，唔好惹到病就ok?<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;呢個邏輯套落《香港01》度係一樣！&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n-香港01紅底咁又點姐？ 咁佢有九成新聞都正常既（九成時間愛你）<br />\n-我哋有分析能力咪得囉 （戴套），唔會咁易被洗腦 （惹性病）<br />\n<br />\n香港01最撚賤係乜？<br />\n佢九成時間講人話，然後係度帶風向<br />\n關鍵時刻就消毒、抹黑，篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />11月都黎喇，團結杯葛香港01啦<br />\n講到口臭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dbf66b541e9467f7c8261e5c8cc7325b86455c","tid":1716973,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"以為小說章節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449f9ba15f17d861eb2db66ddbe40d943c54d3f7","tid":1716973,"uid":86592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:35:07.000Z","msg":"大腸照常升起"},{"pid":"d48f24ac760da1874eaa96efbee7d1c7fe399a22","tid":1716973,"uid":281483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"被清算"},{"pid":"62d68a656cae28dd82557e30c88dcf66eaa24584","tid":1716973,"uid":35580,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"12288024ec2b93d3a7ec2f52efebcb5f62e4a87d","tid":1716973,"uid":53003,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:18:41.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢《決定》？支那啲中文又臭又長，然後又要縮寫，戇鳩鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:35:54.000Z","msg":"d支那文成撚日講野講到痾屎唔出咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc4f3ab9263c058bec29eaaf2a6e7453a988298","tid":1716973,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl